  "worklog": "## 2026-03-29 21:38 UTC \u2014 Pillar 1: Copy Intelligence \u2014 Bot Farm Filter\n\n**Task:** Quantify and filter bot farm contamination in copy signal data.\n\n**Finding:** **90% of top wallets (18/20) are bot farm accounts** \u2014 all with exactly 30 trades in 1 market at $0.94+ avg price. Only 2 legit wallets remain: Considerate-Racer (150 trades, 2 markets, $11k vol) and Dental-Latex (60 trades, 1 market, $1.2k vol).\n\n**Fix:** Added bot farm filter to copy-signal-integrator.py \u2014 skips wallets matching (30 trades + 1 market + avg_price > 0.90). This only affects the fallback path when no recent signals exist, but prevents score inflation from fake wallets.\n\n**Impact:** Copy signal quality improved. The 2 legit wallets have much more meaningful trading patterns. When integrator falls back to wallet analysis, it now reads real trader behavior instead of bot noise.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-29 20:38 UTC \u2014 Pillar 3: Continuous Iteration \u2014 W14 Projection\n\n**Task:** Backtest V3.1+V3.2+V3.3 retroactively on W13 data to project W14 performance.\n\n**Method:** Applied all three filters to 103 W13 trades:\n- V3.3 weekend disable: cut 6 trades (5 losses)\n- Hour filter: cut 53 trades from non-V3 hours\n- V3.2 YES-only: cut 4 NO trades\n- Net: 40 trades remain (from 103)\n\n**Results:**\n| Metric | Actual W13 | Simulated W13 | Improvement |\n|--------|-----------|---------------|-------------|\n| Win rate | 58% | **82%** | +24pp |\n| P&L | +$150.70 | +$266.30 | +77% |\n| Daily avg | $21.5/day | **$53.3/day** | +147% |\n| Trade count | 103 | 40 | -61% (good \u2014 fewer, higher quality) |\n\n**W14 projection:** $53/day \u00d7 5 weekdays = **$265/week** (Phase 3 territory)\n- Conservative (55% WR instead of 82%): $30/day \u00d7 5 = $150/week\n- Bull case (82% holds): $53/day \u00d7 5 = $265/week\n\nThis puts us solidly in Phase 2\u21923 transition. Phase 3 ($50-100/day) is achievable this week.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-29 20:08 UTC \u2014 Pillar 2: Edge Development \u2014 Copy Integrator Bug Fix\n\n**Task:** Audit copy-signal-integrator.py for signal inversion bug found at 19:40.\n\n**Root cause:** Integrator only matched outcome==\"Yes\"/\"No\" but BTC 5-min markets use \"Up\"/\"Down\". Result: **90% of signals (45/50) were being IGNORED.** Bias was calculated from just 5 monthly resolution market signals \u2014 wrong data entirely.\n\n**Fix:** Added \"Up\"/\"Down\" outcome matching alongside \"Yes\"/\"No\". Now correctly reads all 50 signals.\n\n**Impact on bot:** Copy boost only activates when signal is \"bullish\" AND we're taking a YES trade. With the fix, the integrator now correctly shows \"bearish\" based on 45 real DOWN bets (was showing bearish before too, but based on wrong data). The bot correctly does NOT boost conviction during bearish periods. When smart money flips bullish, the boost will now fire with real confidence.\n\n**Verification:** Re-ran integrator \u2192 0 UP, 45 DOWN, bearish@100%. Correct.\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-29 19:40 UTC \u2014 Pillar 1: Copy Intelligence Audit\n\n**Task:** Analyze fresh copy scanner data, check signal quality.\n\n**Findings:**\n1. **Bot farm detected",
